{
  "texts": [
    "The students using traditional methods had to search for, evaluate, and cite sources manually, which allowed them to develop stronger skills in managing bibliographies and critically evaluating the sources used.",
    "This highlights one of ChatGPT main limitations: its inability to perform an exhaustive analysis of the quality and relevance of sources, and its tendency to provide responses without proper management of academic references.Another aspect worth discussing is the fact that the criteria of content depth and problem-solving ability showed minimal differences between the two groups.",
    "Although the experimental group had a slight advantage, these results suggest that using ChatGPT does not guarantee deeper analysis or enhanced problem-solving skills.",
    "This may be due to the fact that, while ChatGPT facilitates access to information and quickly generates ideas, its ability to promote deep critical thinking is limited compared to traditional methods, which require greater cognitive effort from students as they manually search for, analyze, and synthesize information.",
    "The study on the impact of using ChatGPT on achieving research competencies in regular basic education students revealed significant findings in three key dimensions."
  ]
}